</taxonomicName>
was originally described by Lesueur [C. A.] 1821:3, pl. 3 [Journal of the Academy of Natural Sciences, Philadelphia v. 2 (pt 1)] from freshwater ponds in the vicinity of New Orleans, 
<collectingRegion id="4996C3BF0978B226E925F89725934D4C" box="[1319,1432,1867,1893]" country="United States of America" name="Louisiana" pageId="44" pageNumber="495">Louisiana</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingCountry id="F3454DCD0978B226EC95F8B320EF4DA0" box="[151,228,1903,1929]" name="United States of America" pageId="44" pageNumber="495">U.S.A.</collectingCountry>
</paragraph>
